CALL - 3 JUNIOR RESEARCHER POSITIONS:

An international tender to fulfill 3 vacancies for the position of
Junior Researcher in the field of Mathematics, is open for 10 working
days following the publication of the present notice in Di??rio da
Rep??blica [Official Journal of the Portuguese Republic, 30/07/2020]. The
stated position will be held under a public service employment contract
of specified duration at University of Coimbra, Faculty of Sciences and
Technology, UNIT 324 - Centro de Matem??tica da UC (CMUC), under the
Project UIDP/00324/2020.

Public tender reference: IT057-20-10081

Place of Work: University of Coimbra, Faculdade de Ci??ncias e
Tecnologia, UNIDADE 324 - Centro de Matem??tica da UC

Job description: The Junior Researchers will contribute for the
development of CMUC project during the period 2020-2023, in particular
of the CMUC research group in which they will be integrated. The tasks
involved include: (a) Participation in the activities of CMUC with their
specialized expertise; (b) Develop research tasks integrated in one of
the research groups of CMUC (Algebra and Combinatorics; Algebra, Logic
and Topology; Analysis; Geometry; Numerical Analysis and Optimization;
Probability and Statistics); (c) Production and edition of scientific
papers and progress reports of their research work; (d) Supervision of
PhD students in topics covered by CMUC project; (e) Participation in the
outreach activities of CMUC.

Contract length: three-year contract.

For more information see the official announcement at

http://www.eracareers.pt/opportunities/index.aspx?task=global&jobId=125891

Deadline for applications: 13 August 2020.



